\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee51841b3128afb9c231ccb261bb39a4dd858ff0","tid":212392,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T01:42:14.000Z","msg":"認真 天橋立 <br />\n日本三景之一"},{"pid":"3e311ec17fee3c76be6ca436a4bcd86c67e416bc","tid":212392,"uid":37129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T01:59:32.000Z","msg":"江之島，值得一去。特別係佢隔離，係鎌倉好近好近既長谷寺，入面有個洞，好多佛。同一般睇到既日本寺廟唔同，好震撼。/鎌倉高校d女正到仆街。果度有架電車，同電車道。櫻木花道曾經係電車道對面等晴子個情景。好多人係果個點影相。<br />\nskytree，唔撚好去。伏到仆街。<br />\n河口湖，見仁見智。我真係覺得一般既日本景。係網上流傳d圖影到個湖好靚。另外入面，好似有個叫山中湖既地方，我就係遲左去，無得上船，船上可以睇到逆富士，稱之日本一絕景。<br />\n唯有帶點遺憾，以後同重要既人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打可以上網搵下呢個點既料。<br />\n<br />\n要買野去涉谷，真心<br />\n入面既zara. 4ever21等等，雖然香港都有，但人地d款靚一百萬倍。同埋size係俾aisan著既。唔似hk，s碼對於我黎講好大。 wego呢個日本brand值得一去。我都買左好多。Gu雖然hk開左間。但係日本我始終覺得佢價錢係最低，加d款係靚hk好多。uniqlo我無去。<br />\n<br />\n暫時係咁多。<br />\n<br />\n係東京訓醒既早上答你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf481b0c5215cea13d81c7d2d715a9e14b8dc8a","tid":212392,"uid":37129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T02:01:02.000Z","msg":"btw，江之島d人話係貓島，但我一隻都見不到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能d貓貓係集中係某幾點，但我唔經"},{"pid":"81b6b7a8143f79643ab62144e893a479447f760c","tid":212392,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T02:02:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw，江之島d人話係貓島，但我一隻都見不到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能d貓貓係集中係某幾點，但我唔經</blockquote><br />\n我都係想撚下貓 但貓毛都唔見隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de91f0e9fff0b18312b62084784c321d16136c7","tid":212392,"uid":37129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T02:03:30.000Z","msg":"涉谷既迷思。未去之前，我以為好似mk咁。原來唔係，勁都市化得黎，又高級。<br />\n同埋果條全球最多人行既十字路口，真係令我為之一嘆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc3a617e2233d592f91e73c5ec1190d571be2409","tid":212392,"uid":37129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T02:04:32.000Z","msg":"涉谷唔去唔好話去過東京<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> sor，我太激動<br />\nshopping者天堂"},{"pid":"25799e70539592c648882a68e46dee6ae62112eb","tid":212392,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T02:04:38.000Z","msg":"去江之島，分分鐘見香港人仲多過見日本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c495b195949619a5b6364dac25da1f8067a61e75","tid":212392,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T02:08:03.000Z","msg":"稚內好正"},{"pid":"b793f2c7ade1a9b6e424479ffe9206393a255e0f","tid":212392,"uid":37129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T02:08:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去江之島，分分鐘見香港人仲多過見日本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁都唔關個景事既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8dd93b310203f23ed42c5eff43ed576110276a3","tid":212392,"uid":30478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T02:10:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>箱根<br />\n有溫泉、自然地貌:: 蘆之湖、大涌谷</blockquote><br />\n買張pass玩晒海賊船遊湖，纜車上大涌谷，好天可以望到富士山</blockquote><br />\n張PASS堅好用<br />\n因為要由箱根開始搭車上大涌谷, 落返湖, 搭船, 由箱根町去返你酒店既地方<br />\n起碼搭6-8程交通工具<br />\n張PASS包晒"},{"pid":"5ce58a1e6a866142664403fdcee9331507ac6f07","tid":212392,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T02:11:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去江之島，分分鐘見香港人仲多過見日本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁都唔關個景事既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但心情即刻"},{"pid":"827ccff311fe983fe5